drivers: clk: st: Add CLK_GET_RATE_NOCACHE flag to clocks

Add the CLK_GET_RATE_NOCACHE flag to all the clocks with recalc ops,
so that they reflect Hw rate after CPS wake-up when a clk_get_rate()
is called

